<p>Cultural Services offers a variety of arts, culture and heritage services throughout the City and within the new <a href="http://anvilcentre.com/"><strong>Anvil Centre</strong></a>.</p>
<p>Besides direct service delivery, Cultural Services supports and partners with artists, organizations and business to promote arts, culture and heritage in New Westminster.</p>
<p>For a listing our arts, culture and heritage services, please visit our <a href="http://www.newwestpcr.ca/recreation/active-living-guide-and-brochures"><strong>Active Living Guide</strong></a> webpage or our <a href="http://www.newwestpcr.ca/culture/events.php"><strong>Events Calendar. </strong></a></p>
<p>You can also visit our <a href="http://www.newwestculturalmap.ca/" target="_new"><strong>Cultural Map</strong></a> to learn more about the vibrant arts community in New Westminster.</p>
